<td class="article-body"><P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US">Davis</SPAN></B></st1:place></st1:City><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"> Cup -2006<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=PT style="mso-ansi-language: PT">Semi-final Russia vs USA - </SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US">Press Conference - 19.09.2006<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><A href="http://www.alltennis.ru/observatory/?p=36"><U><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3><STRONG>http://www.alltennis.ru/observatory/?p=36</STRONG></FONT></U></A><BR><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">The captain of the USA-team said you have a wide range of players, who you’re able to nominate to play. Have you already chosen who’ll play?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>S.T: </STRONG>Korolev (laughing) Russian tennis is on the rise. We’re in second place according to the number of people playing. That’s a pleasant fact. As for the matches, the chances are equal, everything can happen, because there’s a hard season behind, and as for the form of the players – it will be revealed in the next few days. The one, who’ll be in his best condition, will play.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Reuters: the question to the captain…<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>You’re late. You should always ask first.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Reuters: Can you comment on the information published in a newspaper, which said that Kolya is in bad form, and Marat’s not ready.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>That’s probably a question to Davydenko, not to me. And what newspaper was it?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Reuters: “Zhizn” (Life) or something of that kind…<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>Death…<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Well, there are more serious newspapers. We’re grateful to Davydenko, that he’s humorous about all this.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Misha: </STRONG>You, man of humor, answer it<STRONG>.</STRONG> <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Kolya: </STRONG>Firstly, it’s Tuesday today (pause), and it will be clear, who’ll play, on Thursday. No more comments.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Marat, you had an unusual image before, and now you’ve reverted to the old one. What comes first – the image or the game?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat:</STRONG> I hope you’re not from “Zhizn” (Life)-newspaper? (laughter)<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">NO, Marat, why, you know me well.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat:</STRONG> No. Tennis doesn’t influence the image. You just look for any way to start playing again, to return to the Top 10. So, I try to look for it on court as well as out of it. Just don’t give me away to “Zhizn” (Life) (laughs)<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Misha, you’ve won against Brian brothers at the US Open, will it be possible to outplay them here? <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Misha: </STRONG>That’s good, that I played against them at the US Open. Now I see that it’s possible to defeat them. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>Traditionally we don’t have a doubles team, so it will be decided after the singles matches, depending on how hard each of them will be.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Marat, you’re a big guy, are you digging the court, or what? The American team says there’re some pits in it.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>The court was recently made up, and it’ll be a good one. We’ve talked to the guys who are building it, and they said that the court will be ok by Friday. There’ll be different bounces on it. I don’t think that if we had chosen hard, we would have made the right choice; someone’s got to suffer a bit.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">The captain of the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:country-region w:st="on">US</st1:country-region></st1:place> team said that clay doesn’t suit both them and us. Don’t you think that such a crumbly court can stand in the way to us?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>Comparing with the practice court, the central one is worse because it was made up later. It takes time for the court to settle. We’re experienced in making up courts, so I’m sure that it will be better by the time of the match. This very court exactly makes the chances equal.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Who experiences greater psychological pressure</STRONG>, <STRONG>you’re playing at home after all. <o:p></o:p></STRONG></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Kolya: </STRONG>We’re much more pressured, because we’re playing at home. People expect the victory from us. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Reuters: Roddick said he thinks you’re gonna play both singles matches. Who among the players is more ready?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST:</STRONG> On one hand, there is really some choice. Who’ll play will be decided on Tuesday. Everyone has training sessions twice a day, and time will show who’s more ready. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>All of you have played well at the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:country-region w:st="on">US</st1:country-region></st1:place> Open, do you think male tennis is on the rise, like female is now?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>We can’t compare male tennis with female. Considering male tennis the level of the female one is still a long way off. There are 15 girls in the top 100, and us...the ones in the top 100, are all sitting here.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Dima: </STRONG>you’re 104<SUP>th</SUP>…<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>Dima’s our genius.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">But at the US Open all of us have played well, I’ve found my game and returned to the top 100.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>Ask something to Tursunov. He’s just sitting, showing off his intelligence. Stand up! He wants to read his blog to you!<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Your writing is remarkable. Will you have time to write something during the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Davis</st1:City></st1:place> cup?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Mitya:</STRONG> It depends on who’ll play. If I won’t, I’ll have enough time to write something. I won’t tell you how I write, you’re journalists after all. Secrets, you know. (laughter) And I’m not gonna give you lessons. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Mitya, you’re the smartest player on the tour. Tolstoy also played tennis and as a great writer, may be you’ll be the tennis-Tolstoy?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Mitya: </STRONG>First of all, with an English accent, Tolstoy means fat.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>And I’m far from Tolstoy, though I’m young yet.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Misha, during the interview at the <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">US</st1:place></st1:country-region> Open you said that you would follow the match Spartak vs. CSKA. CSKA lost then and you did too.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>CSKA will play vs. Loko this weekend, will you follow this match?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Misha: </STRONG>Don’t draw a parallel between my match and the loss of CSKA. If CSKA doesn’t win, that doesn’t mean that we won’t win.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>May be we should announce who’ll play according to the result of CSKA. Remember, we still have Zhenya Korlev not involved. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">You were 8 years old, and played in “Olimpiysky”, and you’re gonna play now. Are you more nervous now?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Zhenya: </STRONG>I think I was more nervous that time, because I was young and didn’t want to lose. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">A question to Marat. May I?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>Ah? Am I still interesting to you? (laughter)<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">The season wasn’t quite successful. Will the victory in the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Davis</st1:City></st1:place> Cup add to your personal motivation?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>That’s my only hope this year. Because if we win, the finals will more likely be held in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Moscow</st1:City></st1:place>. The team is in the best form. Kolya plays well, Misha plays well, we’ve got a talented reserve, Korolev. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>ST: </STRONG>You forgot about Dima.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat:</STRONG> He’s a genius. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">So, I’ll concentrate on the Davis Cup, and it will be one more title in my collection. This would be great. This would be the most outstanding victory for the past year and a half. There’re literally a few tournaments left, the end of the season, and I haven’t won anything this year yet. There were two semifinals and the 4<SUP>th</SUP> round of the US Open. I think it’s a big progress.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I was 104<SUP>th</SUP>, it was a no-go. Now it seems to have changed.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>I’d love to gain an optimum shape to start next year in <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Australia</st1:place></st1:country-region> seriously. I like playing there. Let’s hope that next year will go without injuries, and the next 4 years till the end of my career I’ll carry out on a high level. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><STRONG><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Why 4 years?<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><o:p><STRONG><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></STRONG></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><STRONG>Marat: </STRONG>Because it’s hard to think about something more. By then I’ll be 30, then I should take a decision whether I continue playing or I quit and take up some other interesting occupation. You need to consider the right moment. There wont be much pleasure in just running around the court, besides all these flights, hotels. I’ve been playing for 8 years already, I’ll play 4 more years and it’ll be 12. I need to make a decision. Naturally, I’ll continue playing if I wish. Let’s see, how it’ll go. I hope we’ll win the <st1:City w:st="on">Davis</st1:City> cup with this very team in 4 years, we’ll play in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Moscow</st1:City></st1:place>, and it will be a beautiful finish. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P><o:p>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><BR><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><EM>(My thanks to Katherine for the translation and Alexandra for organising it)</EM></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="mso-ansi-language: EN-US"><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><EM><o:p></o:p></EM></FONT></FONT></SPAN></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P></td>
